name: PMQViewer
body:
### PMQ Viewer
PMQ Viewer is an application used to view and manipulate PMQ Files for the Interactive Intelligence System. PMQ Stands for Persistent Message Queue.

```
This application can view both LogBase and I3DBTran Files
```

### Authors and Contributors
This project is created and maintained by William Davis @wjdavis5
